    "answer_id" : 28508114,
    "question_id" : 28505097,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>What you're typing are not normal block comments (/* ... */) but Javadoc comments (/** ... */), and those <em>should</em> have a * at every line. So just delete the extra * after the first / and you'll be fine.</p>\n"
